<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.893844>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 28. Podalonia andrei (F. Morawitz, 1889). Paralectotype ♂: 15 – 22. Lectotype ♀: 23 – 28. 15, 23 — general view, labels; 16, 24 — face; 17, 25 — head lateral; 18, 26 — mesosoma lateral; 19, 27 — mesonotum; 20 — genitalia ventral; 21 — genitalia dorsal; 22 — penis valve lateral; 28 — foretarsus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/893844/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

